<h3>OT booking</h3>
<p>
  After completion of the investment task the Initiator for whom the Investment order was opened,
  completes the fixed asset acceptance form in the OT application.
</p>
<p>
  INFOSYS verifies the data on the OT document, checks the completeness of the attachments,
  assigns the inventory number of the fixed asset, completes the information on the depreciation rate,
  depreciation periods and sends it back to the owner for approval.
</p>
<p>
  If the owner has no objections, he accepts the verified OT document, which is sent to Pune for posting.
</p>
